#: src/buildings.c:33
msgid ""
"The Larn Revenue Service has ordered us to not do business with tax evaders. "
"They have also told us that you owe back taxes and, as we must comply with "
"the law, we cannot serve you at this time.\n"
"\n"
"So Sorry."
msgstr ""
"Le Service des Impôts de Larn nous a ordonné de ne pas commercer avec les "
"fraudeurs du fisc. Il nous a également signalé que vous avez des arriérés "
"d'impôts et, comme nous devons respecter la loi, nous ne pouvons pas vous "
"servir pour le moment.\n"
"\n"
"Toutes nos excuses."

#: src/buildings.c:81
msgid "First National Bank of Larn"
msgstr "Première Banque Nationale de Larn"

#: src/buildings.c:82
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Welcome to the First National Bank of Larn.`end`\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`Bienvenue à la Première Banque Nationale de Larn.`end`\n"
"\n"

#: src/buildings.c:84
msgid ""
"Welcome to the 5th level branch office of the First National Bank of Larn.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Bienvenue à l'agence du cinquième niveau de la Première Banque Nationale de "
"Larn.\n"
"\n"

#: src/buildings.c:87
#, c-format
msgid ""
"The Larn Revenue Service has ordered that your account be frozen until all "
"levied taxes have been paid.  They have also told us that you owe %d gold in "
"taxes, and we must comply with them. We cannot serve you at this time. "
"Sorry.\n"
"\n"
"We suggest you go to the LRS office and pay your taxes."
msgstr ""
"Le Service des Impôts de Larn a ordonné le gel de ton compte jusqu'au "
"paiement de tous les impôts exigés. Il nous a aussi indiqué que tu dois %d "
"d'or d'impôts, et nous devons nous y conformer. Nous ne pouvons pas te "
"servir pour le moment. Désolé.\n"
"\n"
"Nous te suggérons de te rendre au bureau des impôts et de payer ce que tu "
"dois."

#: src/buildings.c:104
#, c-format
msgid "We have paid you an interest of %d gold since your last visit.\n"
msgstr "Nous t'avons versé %d d'or d'intérêts depuis ta dernière visite.\n"

#: src/buildings.c:108
#, c-format
msgid "The bank has paid you an interest of %d gold since your last visit."
msgstr "La banque t'a versé %d d'or d'intérêts depuis ta dernière visite."

#: src/buildings.c:131
#, c-format
msgid ""
"You have %d gold pieces in the bank.\n"
"You have %d gold pieces.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Tu as %d pièces d'or à la banque.\n"
"Tu portes %d pièces d'or.\n"
"\n"

#: src/buildings.c:135
msgid "Your wish? "
msgstr "Ton souhait? "

#: src/buildings.c:146
msgid "`KEY`d`end`)eposit "
msgstr "`KEY`d`end`)époser"

#: src/buildings.c:152
msgid "`KEY`w`end`)ithdraw "
msgstr "`KEY`r`end`)etirer"

#: src/buildings.c:159
msgid "`KEY`s`end`)ell a gem"
msgstr "`KEY`v`end`)endre une gemme"

#: src/buildings.c:175
msgid "How many gold pieces do you wish to deposit?"
msgstr "Combien de pièces d'or veux-tu déposer?"

#: src/buildings.c:182
#, c-format
msgid "You deposited %d gold."
msgstr "Tu as déposé %d d'or."

#: src/buildings.c:189
msgid "You don't have that much."
msgstr "Tu n'en as pas autant."

#: src/buildings.c:198
msgid "How many gold pieces do you wish to withdraw?"
msgstr "Combien de pièces d'or veux-tu retirer?"

#: src/buildings.c:209
#, c-format
msgid "You withdraw %d gold."
msgstr "Tu retires %d d'or."

#: src/buildings.c:219
msgid "You don't have that much in the bank!"
msgstr "Tu n'en as pas autant à la banque!"

#: src/buildings.c:233 src/buildings.c:934
msgid "(`KEY`s`end`)ell"
msgstr "(`KEY`v`end`)endre"

#: src/buildings.c:234
msgid "Sell the currently selected gem."
msgstr "Vends la gemme sélectionnée."

#: src/buildings.c:242
msgid "Sell gems"
msgstr "Vendre des gemmes"

#: src/buildings.c:270
msgid "DND store"
msgstr "Bazar DND"

#: src/buildings.c:271
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Welcome to the Larn Thrift Shoppe.`end`\n"
"\n"
"We stock many items explorers find useful in their adventures. Feel free to "
"browse to your heart's content. Also be advised that if you break 'em, you "
"pay for 'em."
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`Bienvenue à la Friperie de Larn.`end`\n"
"\n"
"Nous tenons en stock quantité d'articles que les explorateurs trouvent "
"utiles dans leurs aventures. N'hésite pas à fouiner à ta guise. Et sache-le: "
"qui casse paie."

#: src/buildings.c:356
msgid "Your home"
msgstr "Ta maison"

#: src/buildings.c:358
#, c-format
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Welcome home, %s.`end`\n"
"\n"
"Latest word from the doctor is not good. The diagnosis is confirmed as "
"dianthroritis. He guesses that your daughter has only %d mobuls left in this "
"world. It's up to you, %s, to find the only hope for your daughter, the very "
"rare potion of cure dianthroritis.  It is rumored that only deep in the "
"depths of the caves can this potion be found.\n"
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`Bienvenue chez toi, %s.`end`\n"
"\n"
"Les dernières nouvelles du docteur ne sont pas bonnes. Le diagnostic est "
"confirmé: dianthroritis. Il estime qu'il ne reste à ta fille que %d mobuls "
"en ce monde. C'est à toi, %s, de trouver le seul espoir pour ta fille: la "
"très rare potion de guérison de la dianthroritis. La rumeur veut que cette "
"potion ne se trouve qu'au plus profond des cavernes.\n"

#: src/buildings.c:367
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Congratulations!`end` You found the potion of cure dianthroritis! "
"Frankly, No one thought you could do it. Boy! Did you surprise them!\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`Félicitations!`end` Tu as trouvé la potion de guérison de la "
"dianthroritis! Franchement, personne ne t'en croyait capable. Quelle "
"surprise tu leur as faite!\n"
"\n"

#: src/buildings.c:371
msgid ""
"The doctor has the sad duty to inform you that your daughter died before "
"your return. There was nothing he could do without the potion.\n"
"\n"
"You didn't make it in time. Too bad..."
msgstr ""
"Le docteur a le triste devoir de t'informer que ta fille est morte avant ton "
"retour. Sans la potion, il ne pouvait rien faire.\n"
"\n"
"Tu n'es pas arrivé à temps. Quel dommage..."

#: src/buildings.c:376
msgid ""
"The doctor is now administering the potion and, in a few moments, your "
"daughter should be well on her way to recovery.\n"
"\n"
"The potion is working! The doctor thinks that your daughter will recover in "
"a few days.\n"
"\n"
"Congratulations!"
msgstr ""
"Le docteur administre la potion et, dans quelques instants, ta fille devrait "
"être en bonne voie de guérison.\n"
"\n"
"La potion agit! Le docteur pense que ta fille sera rétablie dans quelques "
"jours.\n"
"\n"
"Félicitations!"

#: src/buildings.c:394 src/player.c:1116
msgid "You saved your daughter!"
msgstr "Tu as sauvé ta fille!"

#: src/buildings.c:414 src/buildings.c:425
msgid "You were too late!"
msgstr "Tu es arrivé trop tard!"

#: src/buildings.c:453
msgid "`KEY`d`end`)eposit something here"
msgstr "`KEY`d`end`)époser quelque chose ici"

#: src/buildings.c:459
msgid "`KEY`t`end`)ake something with you"
msgstr "e`KEY`m`end`)porter quelque chose"

#: src/buildings.c:478
msgid "(`KEY`d`end`)eposit"
msgstr "(`KEY`d`end`)époser"

#: src/buildings.c:479
msgid "Deposit the selected item in your storage room at home."
msgstr "Dépose l'objet sélectionné dans le débarras de ta maison."

#: src/buildings.c:503
msgid "(`KEY`t`end`)ake"
msgstr "(`KEY`p`end`)rendre"

#: src/buildings.c:504
msgid ""
"Take the selected item out of your storage room and put it into your pack."
msgstr "Prends l'objet sélectionné dans ton débarras et mets-le dans ton sac."

#: src/buildings.c:514
msgid "take (`KEY`a`end`)ll"
msgstr "(`KEY`t`end`)out emporter"

#: src/buildings.c:515
msgid ""
"Take all items from your storage room. Only available when you can carry the "
"total weight."
msgstr ""
"Emporte tous les objets de ton débarras. Seulement possible quand tu peux "
"porter le poids total."

#: src/buildings.c:544
msgid "Larn Revenue Service"
msgstr "Service des Impôts de Larn"

#: src/buildings.c:545
msgid ""
"Welcome to the Larn Revenue Service district office.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Bienvenue au bureau de district du Service des Impôts de Larn.\n"
"\n"

#: src/buildings.c:546
#, c-format
msgid ""
"You presently owe %d gold in taxes.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Tu dois actuellement %d d'or d'impôts.\n"
"\n"

#: src/buildings.c:547
msgid "You do not owe us any taxes."
msgstr "Tu ne nous dois aucun impôt."

#: src/buildings.c:560
msgid "Do you want to pay your taxes?"
msgstr "Veux-tu payer tes impôts?"

#: src/buildings.c:567
msgid "You have paid your taxes."
msgstr "Tu as payé tes impôts."

#: src/buildings.c:571
msgid "You chose not to pay your taxes."
msgstr "Tu as choisi de ne pas payer tes impôts."

#: src/buildings.c:576
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, it seems that you cannot afford to pay your taxes at this "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Hélas, il semble que tu n'aies pas les moyens de payer tes impôts pour le "
"moment."

#: src/buildings.c:602 src/buildings.c:618 src/buildings.c:623
#: src/buildings.c:641 src/buildings.c:652 src/buildings.c:668
#: src/buildings.c:679 src/buildings.c:790
msgid "School"
msgstr "École"

#: src/buildings.c:602
msgid "To craft a scroll, the scribes must first be given a blank one."
msgstr ""
"Pour confectionner un parchemin, il faut d'abord fournir aux scribes un "
"parchemin vierge."

#: src/buildings.c:608
msgid "Choose a scroll to inscribe"
msgstr "Choisis un parchemin à inscrire"

#: src/buildings.c:614 src/buildings.c:623
msgid "Okay then."
msgstr "Bon, d'accord."

#: src/buildings.c:619
msgid "Which incantation shall we bind in ink?"
msgstr "Quelle incantation fixerons-nous dans l'encre?"

#: src/buildings.c:642
msgid ""
"Even the oldest scribes know nothing of a scroll like that. Alas, the scroll "
"must remain blank - for even the greatest scribes cannot write what does not "
"exist."
msgstr ""
"Même les plus anciens scribes ne connaissent pas un tel parchemin. Hélas, le "
"parchemin devra rester vierge - car même les plus grands scribes ne peuvent "
"écrire ce qui n'existe pas."

#: src/buildings.c:652
msgid "A blank scroll, by definition, needs no scribe."
msgstr "Un parchemin vierge, par définition, n'a pas besoin de scribe."

#: src/buildings.c:662
#, c-format
msgid ""
"You do not possess the %d gold necessary to acquire the scroll of %s. For "
"now, the scribes shall keep their quills dry."
msgstr ""
"Tu ne possèdes pas les %d d'or nécessaires pour acquérir le parchemin %s. "
"Pour l'heure, les plumes des scribes resteront sèches."

#: src/buildings.c:674
#, c-format
msgid ""
"The crafting of a scroll of %s demands a fee of %d gold.\n"
"Would that be agreeable to you?"
msgstr ""
"La confection d'un parchemin %s exige des honoraires de %d d'or.\n"
"Cela te convient-il?"

#: src/buildings.c:700
#, c-format
msgid "waiting for the scribes to write a scroll of %s for you"
msgstr "attendre que les scribes te rédigent un parchemin %s"

#: src/buildings.c:704
#, c-format
msgid "The scribes have completed a scroll of %s on your behalf."
msgstr "Les scribes ont achevé un parchemin %s pour toi."

#: src/buildings.c:723
msgid "Fighters Training I"
msgstr "Entraînement au combat I"

#: src/buildings.c:723
msgid "You feel stronger!"
msgstr "Tu te sens plus fort!"

#: src/buildings.c:724
msgid "Fighters Training II"
msgstr "Entraînement au combat II"

#: src/buildings.c:724
msgid "You feel much stronger!"
msgstr "Tu te sens bien plus fort!"

#: src/buildings.c:725
msgid "Introduction to Wizardry"
msgstr "Introduction à la magie"

#: src/buildings.c:725
msgid "The task before you now seems more attainable!"
msgstr "La tâche qui t'attend semble maintenant plus à ta portée!"

#: src/buildings.c:726
msgid "Applied Wizardry"
msgstr "Magie appliquée"

#: src/buildings.c:726
msgid "The task before you now seems very attainable!"
msgstr "La tâche qui t'attend semble maintenant tout à fait à ta portée!"

#: src/buildings.c:727
msgid "Faith for Today"
msgstr "La foi au quotidien"

#: src/buildings.c:727
msgid "You now feel more confident that you can find the potion in time!"
msgstr "Tu as maintenant meilleur espoir de trouver la potion à temps!"

#: src/buildings.c:728
msgid "Contemporary Dance"
msgstr "Danse contemporaine"

#: src/buildings.c:728
msgid "You feel like dancing!"
msgstr "Tu as envie de danser!"

#: src/buildings.c:729
msgid "History of Larn"
msgstr "Histoire de Larn"

#: src/buildings.c:729
msgid ""
"Your instructor told you that the Eye of Larn is rumored to be guarded by an "
"invisible demon lord."
msgstr ""
"Ton professeur t'a raconté que, selon la rumeur, l'Œil de Larn serait gardé "
"par un seigneur démon invisible."

#: src/buildings.c:741
#, c-format
msgid "taking the course \"%s\""
msgstr "suivre le cours «%s»"

#: src/buildings.c:783
#, c-format
msgid "You successfully complete the course \"%s\". %s"
msgstr "Tu termines avec succès le cours «%s». %s"

#: src/buildings.c:791
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Welcome to the College of Larn!`end`\n"
"\n"
"We offer the exciting opportunity of higher education to all inhabitants of "
"the caves. Here is a list of the class schedule:"
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`Bienvenue à l'École de Larn!`end`\n"
"\n"
"Nous offrons la passionnante possibilité d'études supérieures à tous les "
"habitants des cavernes. Voici le programme des cours:"

#: src/buildings.c:832
msgid "You have already attended this course."
msgstr "Tu as déjà suivi ce cours."

#: src/buildings.c:836 src/buildings.c:858
#, c-format
msgid "Duration: %d mobuls"
msgstr "Durée: %d mobuls"

#: src/buildings.c:839
#, c-format
msgid "Cost: %d gold"
msgstr "Coût: %d d'or"

#: src/buildings.c:844
#, c-format
msgid "Requires: %s"
msgstr "Prérequis: %s"

#: src/buildings.c:854
msgid "Commission a scroll"
msgstr "Commander un parchemin"

#: src/buildings.c:891
#, c-format
msgid "You cannot afford the %d gold for the course."
msgstr "Tu n'as pas les moyens de payer les %d d'or du cours."

#: src/buildings.c:910
msgid "Trade Post"
msgstr "Comptoir commercial"

#: src/buildings.c:912
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Welcome to the Larn Trading Post.`end`\n"
"\n"
"We buy items that explorers no longer find useful.\n"
"Since the condition of the items you bring in is not certain, and we incur "
"great expense in reconditioning the items, we usually pay only 20% of their "
"value were they to be new.\n"
"If the items are badly damaged, we will pay only 10% of their new value."
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`Bienvenue au Comptoir commercial de Larn.`end`\n"
"\n"
"Nous rachetons les objets qui ne sont plus utiles aux explorateurs.\n"
"Comme l'état des objets apportés est incertain et que leur remise en état "
"nous coûte cher, nous ne payons d'ordinaire que 20% de leur valeur à neuf.\n"
"Si les objets sont très abîmés, nous n'en payons que 10%."

#: src/buildings.c:935
msgid "Sell the selected item to the Trade Post."
msgstr "Vends l'objet sélectionné au comptoir commercial."

#: src/buildings.c:944
msgid "(`KEY`i`end`)dentify"
msgstr "(`KEY`i`end`)dentifier"

#: src/buildings.c:945
msgid "Have the Trade Post's experts identify your item."
msgstr "Fais identifier ton objet par les experts du comptoir."

#: src/buildings.c:953
msgid "(`KEY`r`end`)epair"
msgstr "(`KEY`r`end`)éparer"

#: src/buildings.c:954
msgid ""
"Have the Trade Post's experts revert any damage done to the selected item."
msgstr ""
"Fais réparer par les experts du comptoir les dommages subis par l'objet "
"sélectionné."

#: src/buildings.c:962 src/player.c:2633
msgid "(`KEY`e`end`)quip"
msgstr "(`KEY`é`end`)quiper"

#: src/buildings.c:963 src/player.c:2634
msgid "Equip the selected item."
msgstr "Équipe l'objet sélectionné."

#: src/buildings.c:970 src/player.c:2657
msgid "(`KEY`u`end`)nequip"
msgstr "(`KEY`d`end`)éséquiper"

#: src/buildings.c:971 src/player.c:2658
msgid "Unequip the selected item."
msgstr "Déséquipe l'objet sélectionné."

#: src/buildings.c:979 src/player.c:2674
msgid "(`KEY`n`end`)ote"
msgstr "(`KEY`n`end`)oter"

#: src/buildings.c:980
msgid "Add a note to the item."
msgstr "Ajoute une note à l'objet."

#: src/buildings.c:999
msgid "The Monastery of Larn"
msgstr "Le monastère de Larn"

#: src/buildings.c:1001
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Welcome, traveler, to the Monastery of Larn.`end`\n"
"\n"
"Peace be upon you. The walls of the monastery offer respite to all who seek "
"it.\n"
"\n"
"Speak your need, and if it lies within our calling, it shall be granted... "
"for a fair offering. We tend the wounded and weary, and offer a small "
"selection of tools and provisions to aid those who walk the road of trials."
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`Bienvenue, voyageur, au monastère de Larn.`end`\n"
"\n"
"Que la paix soit avec toi. Les murs du monastère offrent le repos à "
"quiconque le cherche.\n"
"\n"
"Dis ton besoin, et s'il relève de notre vocation, il sera exaucé... contre "
"une juste offrande. Nous soignons les blessés et les épuisés, et proposons "
"un petit choix d'outils et de provisions pour aider ceux qui suivent le "
"chemin des épreuves."

#: src/buildings.c:1008
msgid "Shall we proceed, then?"
msgstr "Procédons-nous, alors?"

#: src/buildings.c:1027
msgid "poison"
msgstr "l'empoisonnement"

#: src/buildings.c:1033
msgid "blindness"
msgstr "la cécité"

#: src/buildings.c:1039
